title: Chuck Hack | The Rig Out x Margot Bowman | 'Feedback'
description:
Creative Collective The Rig Out teamed with digital artist Margot Bowman to create a special Chuck Hack film, 'Feedback', documenting the unique Kuduro music scene in Lisbon, Portugal.

Adding sensors to dancers' Chucks as they performed to Kuduro legend DJ NK's tracks, 'Feedback' is a project about the feedback loop between creative ideas, technology and creative self expression, mapping the movement of creative energy.
